de.ovgu.featureide.fm.ui.editors.elements

Class TikzGraphicalFeatureModelFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.io.APersistentFormat<IGraphicalFeatureModel>
      • de.ovgu.featureide.fm.ui.editors.elements.TikzGraphicalFeatureModelFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.IExtension, de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.io.IPersistentFormat<IGraphicalFeatureModel>

    public class TikzGraphicalFeatureModelFormat
extends de.ovgu.featureide.fm.core.io.APersistentFormat<IGraphicalFeatureModel>
    This class implements a LaTeX converter for the feature diagram (using TikZ).
    The main class uses one String for the latex code; the subclasses divides the code into three different Strings (each subclass for one String).
    Author:
    Simon Wenk, Yang Liu
